data: {"candidates": [{"content": {"parts": [{"text": "**Sequencing the Numbers**\n\nI'm analyzing the user's request, focusing on identifying the pattern in the sequence: 2, 6, 12, 20, 30. The explicit request for \"reasoning\" is a crucial prompt to ensure I present the explanation. I'm aiming to articulate a method for generating the numbers.\n\n\n","thought": true}],"role": "model"},"index": 0,"safetyRatings": [{"category": "HARM_CATEGORY_SEXUALLY_EXPLICIT","probability": "NEGLIGIBLE"},{"category": "HARM_CATEGORY_HATE_SPEECH","probability": "NEGLIGIBLE"},{"category": "HARM_CATEGORY_HARASSMENT","probability": "NEGLIGIBLE"},{"category": "HARM_CATEGORY_DANGEROUS_CONTENT","probability": "NEGLIGIBLE"}]}],"usageMetadata": {"promptTokenCount": 34,"totalTokenCount": 103,"promptTokensDetails": [{"modality": "TEXT","tokenCount": 34}],"thoughtsTokenCount": 69},"modelVersion": "gemini-2.5-pro","responseId": "2zB1afLeH82MjMcPn6aWsAY"}

data: {"candidates": [{"content": {"parts": [{"text": "**Unveiling the Pattern**\n\nI've determined the next number is 42. I noticed the differences between consecutive terms form an arithmetic progression (4, 6, 8, 10), increasing by 2 each time. Thus, the next difference is 12, adding it to 30. Now I plan to structure the response, starting with the answer then including the step-by-step reasoning.\n\n\n","thought": true}],"role": "model"},"index": 0,"safetyRatings": [{"category": "HARM_CATEGORY_SEXUALLY_EXPLICIT","probability": "NEGLIGIBLE"},{"category": "HARM_CATEGORY_HATE_SPEECH","probability": "NEGLIGIBLE"},{"category": "HARM_CATEGORY_HARASSMENT","probability": "NEGLIGIBLE"},{"category": "HARM_CATEGORY_DANGEROUS_CONTENT","probability": "NEGLIGIBLE"}]}],"usageMetadata": {"promptTokenCount": 34,"totalTokenCount": 453,"promptTokensDetails": [{"modality": "TEXT","tokenCount": 34}],"thoughtsTokenCount": 419},"modelVersion": "gemini-2.5-pro","responseId": "2zB1afLeH82MjMcPn6aWsAY"}

data: {"candidates": [{"content": {"parts": [{"text": "**Discovering the Formula**\n\nI'm now investigating alternative representations. I've realized the sequence consists of products of consecutive integers: 2 = 1\\*2, 6 = 2\\*3, 12 = 3\\*4, and so on. This pattern, (n\\*(n+1)), is the formula I am honing to present a concise, insightful explanation.\n\n\n","thought": true}],"role": "model"},"index": 0,"safetyRatings": [{"category": "HARM_CATEGORY_SEXUALLY_EXPLICIT","probability": "NEGLIGIBLE"},{"category": "HARM_CATEGORY_HATE_SPEECH","probability": "NEGLIGIBLE"},{"category": "HARM_CATEGORY_HARASSMENT","probability": "NEGLIGIBLE"},{"category": "HARM_CATEGORY_DANGEROUS_CONTENT","probability": "NEGLIGIBLE"}]}],"usageMetadata": {"promptTokenCount": 34,"totalTokenCount": 750,"promptTokensDetails": [{"modality": "TEXT","tokenCount": 34}],"thoughtsTokenCount": 716},"modelVersion": "gemini-2.5-pro","responseId": "2zB1afLeH82MjMcPn6aWsAY"}

data: {"candidates": [{"content": {"parts": [{"text": "**Formulating the Explanation**\n\nI'm now building a detailed, well-structured explanation. I plan to present both the \"difference\" method and the consecutive integers multiplication method. I will begin by stating the answer clearly. I also want to make sure I show the step by step reasoning for each method. I think this will provide a complete answer.\n\n\n","thought": true}],"role": "model"},"index": 0,"safetyRatings": [{"category": "HARM_CATEGORY_SEXUALLY_EXPLICIT","probability": "NEGLIGIBLE"},{"category": "HARM_CATEGORY_HATE_SPEECH","probability": "NEGLIGIBLE"},{"category": "HARM_CATEGORY_HARASSMENT","probability": "NEGLIGIBLE"},{"category": "HARM_CATEGORY_DANGEROUS_CONTENT","probability": "NEGLIGIBLE"}]}],"usageMetadata": {"promptTokenCount": 34,"totalTokenCount": 850,"promptTokensDetails": [{"modality": "TEXT","tokenCount": 34}],"thoughtsTokenCount": 816},"modelVersion": "gemini-2.5-pro","responseId": "2zB1afLeH82MjMcPn6aWsAY"}

data: {"candidates": [{"content": {"parts": [{"text": "Of course! The next number in the sequence is **42**.\n\nHere are a couple of ways to see"}],"role": "model"},"index": 0,"safetyRatings": [{"category": "HARM_CATEGORY_SEXUALLY_EXPLICIT","probability": "NEGLIGIBLE"},{"category": "HARM_CATEGORY_HATE_SPEECH","probability": "NEGLIGIBLE"},{"category": "HARM_CATEGORY_HARASSMENT","probability": "NEGLIGIBLE"},{"category": "HARM_CATEGORY_DANGEROUS_CONTENT","probability": "NEGLIGIBLE"}]}],"usageMetadata": {"promptTokenCount": 34,"candidatesTokenCount": 19,"totalTokenCount": 869,"promptTokensDetails": [{"modality": "TEXT","tokenCount": 34}],"thoughtsTokenCount": 816},"modelVersion": "gemini-2.5-pro","responseId": "2zB1afLeH82MjMcPn6aWsAY"}

